249-01||21||There is no active abductor pollicis brevis and  very weak opponens.
249-01||22||He has a positive Tinel's, positive Phalen's, and positive median nerve compression test at the wrist.
249-01||23||His interossei and extensors are full.
249-01||24||Sensation is intact throughout.
